11.   Normalization 
12.   Normalization (Scores to DT_R8 (or DT_NUMERIC) in data conversion)
min-max     ([Scores] - 50) / (100 - 50)
z-score     ([Scores] - 70) / 15
13.      [CountryCode] == "US" ? "United States" : ([CountryCode] == "IN" ? "India" : ([CountryCode] == "UK" ? "United Kingdom" : ([CountryCode] == "CA" ? "Canada" : "Unknown")))
14.    Cur_agr      (DT_I4)(DATEDIFF("day",(DT_DATE)date_of_birth,GETDATE()) / 365.25)
16.    'YYYY-MM-DD' → 'DD-MM-YYYY'   SUBSTRING([DateColumn], 9, 2) + "-" + SUBSTRING([DateColumn], 6, 2) + "-" + SUBSTRING([DateColumn], 1, 4)
        'DD-MM-YYYY' → 'YYYY-MM-DD'    SUBSTRING([DateColumn], 7, 4) + "-" + SUBSTRING([DateColumn], 4, 2) + "-" + SUBSTRING([DateColumn], 1, 2)







